      "description": "Looking for affordable wheels without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great option for someone who needs simple, budget-friendly transportation or a handy project to tinker with. It\u2019s got plenty of character, and for the right buyer, there\u2019s still good value here. If you want an honest, inexpensive car at a fair price, this one is worth a look.",
