      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast upside. Runs and drives, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels fundamentally intact. Suspension, braking, and chassis all present a good starting point for someone who wants a budget-friendly platform to sort, refresh, and make their own. Cosmetically it shows wear and needs attention, but the mechanical package has the kind of honest, usable character that makes it worth the effort. Great candidate for a daily beater, weekend wrenching project, or affordable entry into ownership.",
