      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real grit and presence\u2014the kind of machine that still turns heads for its attitude and honest, lived-in character. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh; instead, it offers an affordable way into dependable transportation with a lot of personality. Perfect for a handy owner, a daily commuter on a budget, or someone looking for a practical project, this one has the kind of charm that comes from miles of stories and plenty more left to tell.",
